Class Photo

java.lang.Object
model.Photo
All Implemented Interfaces:
Serializable
public class Photo extends Object implements Serializable
The Photo class represents a photo that contains a collection of tags. It provides functionality to manage tags, retrieve photo details, and compare photos with each other.

This class implements Serializable to allow serialization of album objects.

Features of the Album class include:

  • Adding and removing tags
  • Retrieving the total number of tags
  • Managing the fields and setting the Date
